msgid "Strategic Hub (Obsidian)"
msgstr "戦略ハブ (Obsidian)"

msgid "The Strategic Hub is the heart of the Spec-Craft workflow. It leverages Obsidian to maintain a high-level creative roadmap that guides all implementation efforts."
msgstr "戦略ハブは、Spec-Craftワークフローの心臓部です。Obsidianを活用して、すべての実装作業を導くハイレベルなクリエイティブロードマップを維持します。"

msgid "Strategy vs Tactics Analogy"
msgstr "戦略 vs 戦術の比喩"

msgid "Understanding the difference between strategy and tactics is key to the Spec-Craft philosophy:"
msgstr "戦略と戦術の違いを理解することは、Spec-Craftの哲学において重要です："

msgid "Strategy (Obsidian):"
msgstr "戦略 (Obsidian)："

msgid "Focus: \"What\" and \"Why\"."
msgstr "焦点： 「何を作るか」「なぜ作るか」"

msgid "Tactics (spec-kit):"
msgstr "戦術 (spec-kit)："

msgid "Focus: \"How\"."
msgstr "焦点： 「どう実装するか」"
